      <p>Values the franchise based on its tangible and intangible assets, including equipment, territory rights, and goodwill.</p>

      <h3>3. Market Approach</h3>
      <p>Compares your franchise to similar franchises that have recently sold in your market.</p>

      <h3>4. Income Approach</h3>
      <p>Projects future cash flows and discounts them to present value.</p>
